snippet.textDisplay: When I watched this video two years back I didn’t know it was a Pakistani video, I couldn’t spot a single thing in the video that could make it distinct from any other Indian music video. Only when I read the comments I came to know it was actually a Pakistani video. Point being that despite years of chaos, art and culture still holds these countries together, making us realise that 1947 se pehle ek hi toh the yaar.
